Saturday night, May 7th: I saw House of Wax and haha it was funny, not really scary.. We werent aloud to go in , we couldnt even sneak in because there were gaurds gaurding all the "R"rated movies.. So all these kids that couldnt go in I was like hey lets all go in together and since my 23 year old sister was at the mall I asked her to come.. and yes she came to get us in.. we all exchanged our tickets for new ones at 8:00pm and yes we ALL got in.. everyone was like omg your sister is the fizzing Shit I <3 her. yes! so yeah it was awsome.. the movie, eh.. wasnt scary.. th whole story was gross though.. about the whole thing with the wax and shit. heh. yeah..
